Red Bolt, holding his arm on, tells Freewing he has an idea. "If we were to 
create an appropriate faction with these Neutral Transformers, we might be 
able to find Rackmaster, that slaggin' coward that attacked us in the 
arctic." Freewing nods, and begins considering Red Bolts proposal.
